            "type": "text",
            "data": "Using a Mouse in the S2M Optimizer"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "You can choose options by left clicking them with your mouse. You also can use the mouse to select objects on the screen. With a two-button mouse, the left button is the select button used to select objects on the screen. The right button typically displays a shortcut menu."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Scroll Wheel Mouse"
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "data": "image164.gif",
            "description": "[Placeholder for AI-generated description]"
