        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "Mouse Button Functions"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "The mouse provides feedback to the S2M Optimizer regarding a variety of functions. Although a Scroll Wheel Mouse is optional, it is highly recommended. The functions are listed below:"
