            "type": "text",
            "data": "A Scroll Wheel Mouse is typically a two-button mouse with a small wheel between the buttons. The left and right buttons behave the same as they do on a standard mouse. You can rotate the wheel by discrete values. You can use the wheel to zoom and pan in your drawing without using any S2M Optimizer tools."
